  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Willing to provide informed consent

          -  Age &gt;= 60 years

          -  Ambulatory

          -  Community-living

          -  Self-reported chronic musculoskeletal pain &gt; 3 months having pain made it difficult to
             do usual activities

          -  Ability to attend sessions one in a week for 6-weeks

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Serious illness or hospitalisation in last 3-month

          -  Planned surgery in next six months

          -  Significant cognitive impairment

          -  Other severe physical or psychiatric disorder
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
